}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== Device is a [[SerComm IP1006SR]] (YPK00A-1.0)
The default SSID appears to be '''Belkin_XXXXXX''' where '''XXXXXX''' is the last three octets of the wireless interface MAC (lower case letters).
The power adapter included with the device is a '''Leader Electronics''' M12-Y1120-A64S (12V, 1A). ID/OD/Len measurements are approximate.
